{"tid":1672331,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【各區攻略】我地需要贏，必須區議會配票","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T16:30:13.000Z","uid":36578,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f16abe2da0e830c770869eaa9631f7595277dfc2","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"2019區議會選舉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家務必配票</span></span>，建立美好的香港家園<br />\n請各區既邨屋必須參加配票<br />\n<br />\n例如：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍田區</span></span>-譚得志(快必)<br />\n配票屋邨：藍田邨、啟田邨、安田邨、平田邨、德田邨<br />\n(以上必須有組織咁去投同一個人)<br />\n<br />\n👍黃之鋒 --- 海怡半島 <br />\n👍韋少力 &mdash;-鯉景灣<br />\n👍鄭達鴻 --- 北角區丹拿<br />\n👍李予信 --- 北角區 <br />\n👍陳嘉陽 --- 北角和富 <br />\n👍傅佳琳 --- 北角堡壘<br />\n👍仇栩欣 --- 北角城市花園<br />\n👍曾因瑩 --- 小西灣景怡<br />\n👍何志宏 --- 水街 <br />\n👍李永財 --- 銅鑼灣<br />\n👍彭家浩 --- 西環區<br />\n👍徐遠華 --- 黃竹坑<br />\n<br />\n👍鄭駿樺 &mdash;- 牛頭角上邨<br />\n👍李詠珊 &mdash;- 牛頭角下邨<br />\n👍蔡澤鴻 --- 觀塘<br />\n👍李梓成 --- 秀茂坪<br />\n👍劉家衡 --- 南   昌<br />\n👍甄啟榮 --- 白   田<br />\n👍黃虹銘 --- 屯門區<br />\n👍童繼民 --- 紅磡海心<br />\n👍岑宇軒 --- 黃大仙<br />\n👍郭秀英 --- 黃大仙<br />\n<br />\n👍曾子麟 --- 葵芳<br />\n👍易承聰 --- 荃灣<br />\n👍曾錦榮 --- 屯門<br />\n👍黄偉賢 --- 元朗<br />\n👍杜嘉倫 --- 錦繡花園<br />\n<br />\n👍曾    杰 --- 沙田新翠<br />\n👍許銳宇 --- 沙田大圍<br />\n<br />\n請大家認清投票名單，以上名單未必最新及最齊全，希望大家合作，請提供你地區既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真．民主區議員</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外要做多啲文宣，邊區投邊個...目標要一致<br />\n<br />\n問各位更新名單，分類區域<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191006/large/1570338958_a270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191006%2Flarge%2F1570338958_a270.jpg&h=a53de415&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a7322a690763680900b758b0c3fd8902e046acb","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"推一推x10"},{"pid":"f9cd422b09b2a090ada362a9c68034fd99946161","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"推一推x9"},{"pid":"85fcaeba6342c3da4999916fc5d3dc7075c84a0e","tid":1672331,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itbR4in.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitbR4in.jpg&h=bd7ae3e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"026e86ad418ff0111b51d3d0d1ce3e3ac027838b","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"推一推x8"},{"pid":"1ed867f1b744bae05faa7eaf443378030b933d1e","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"推一推x7"},{"pid":"af837d6a5a58d673ee1512aa9d4740cf0c8c58c5","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"推一推x6"},{"pid":"03f7f0ba19d7fb610517f9fbc6c5455d0f4db3a7","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"推一推x5"},{"pid":"fbd8aa9d8055d2c0b78e64d850159e9d0cfed3a4","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"推一推x4"},{"pid":"9e7aaeb15199e1d512cd3bcb66f1ec0f21b03a38","tid":1672331,"uid":166982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"596ea75863e54cd464dd9bea835c681ed4f0126b","tid":1672331,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"推一推x3"},{"pid":"8c5b57bbd193d0bd4c0f977fdba99f496e117b16","tid":167233